DTSTAMP:20260326T185921Z
DTSTART:20260813T230000Z
DTEND:20260814T013000Z
SUMMARY:Just In Time
LOCATION:Circle In The Square Theatre, 1633 Broadway / 235 West 50th Street, New York NY 10019
DESCRIPTION:<p><em>Just In Time</em> is an &ldquo;utterly
  electrifying&rdquo; (<em>Entertainment Weekly</em>) new musical that
  brings to life the story of Bobby Darin, the legendary singer whose short
  but remarkable journey took him from teen idol to global sensation.<br
  /><br />Developed and directed by Tony Award&reg; winner Alex Timbers
  (<em>Moulin Rouge!</em>), the show immerses audiences into an intimate
  nightclub &ldquo;so seductive in ambiance that you find yourself not
  wanting to go back outside&rdquo; (<em>Chicago Tribune</em>). Complete
  with iconic hits including &ldquo;Beyond the Sea,&rdquo; &ldquo;Mack the
  Knife,&rdquo; &ldquo;Splish Splash,&rdquo; and &ldquo;Dream Lover,&rdquo;
  <em>Just In Time</em> is &ldquo;a helluva good time at the theater&rdquo;
  (<em>Time Out</em>).</p>
END:VEVENT
